        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Down That Trail in the Woods - Kìzis"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Presented in collaboration with Danse-Cité,Down That Trail in the Woodsis a wildly imaginative musical where theatre, dance, and live music intertwine. Under the direction of Kìzis, 19 performers carry a new story forward, passing through love, loss, and the traces that endure."
      }
    ],
